These examples are all written in Java and compiled with Maven:

    http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi

To build and run, change into the directory of the project and:

    mvn compile
    mvn exec:java
    -----------------
    mvn help:system
    mvn compile
mvn package
java -jar target\xxx.jar
--------------
Simon:
go to the code to javac *.java
to run it, you need first read the code, example:
package com.paulbutcher;

Then you need cd ..\..\

java com.paulbutcher.Counting